{"tid":751383,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"CIA用千里眼'望'倒火星公元前一百萬前個金字塔有'人'","createTime":"2018-07-21T22:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T09:05:02.000Z","uid":165773,"like":12,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"04d2d9c2d3ce900a4c21cde47d6bbb493fe91925","tid":751383,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T22:15:50.000Z","msg":"為左冇咁亂。。。呢post分三個部份<br />\n部份一<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Russell_Targ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FRussell_Targ&d=KVXReHL18IQ%2FliS%2BhPGK%2Fp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=7bc009a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Russell_Targ</a><br />\n<strong>Russell</strong>係美國早期研究laser應用既物理學家<br />\n-1960年代出左起碼7份paper<br />\n-1970年代比CIA請左去史丹福研究超能力<br />\nResearch paper:<br />\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20141023024744/http://www.scientificexploration.org/journal/jse_10_1_targ.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20141023024744%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.scientificexploration.org%2Fjournal%2Fjse_10_1_targ.pdf&d=KVXReHL18IQ%2FliS%2BhPGK%2Fp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=bcb8dd8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://web.archive.org/web/20141023024744/http://www.scientificexploration.org/journal/jse_10_1_targ.pdf</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hBl0cwyn5GY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhBl0cwyn5GY&d=KVXReHL18IQ%2FliS%2BhPGK%2Fp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=9dc2ce3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hBl0cwyn5GY</a><br />\nRussell2013年親自講關於佢當年Stanford做既研究<br />\nCIA一直冇正面confirm有冇超能人存在<br />\n但係2016年CIA公開幾百萬個舊機密文件<br />\n其中一份同Russell講既野 勁吻合<br />\n___________________________<br />\n部份二<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cia.gov/library/readingroom/docs/CIA-RDP96-00788R001900760001-9.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cia.gov%2Flibrary%2Freadingroom%2Fdocs%2FCIA-RDP96-00788R001900760001-9.pdf&d=KVXReHL18IQ%2FliS%2BhPGK%2Fp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=35ca7a98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cia.gov/library/readingroom/docs/CIA-RDP96-00788R001900760001-9.pdf</a><br />\n<strong>CIA舊機密文件內容(9頁)</strong><br />\nMars Exploration（2000年解封，2016先upload左上官網）<br />\n內容係一個CIA人員同有千里眼既subject對話<br />\n（\b冇講千里眼係咪人，文件只係用subject代表）<br />\n<br />\nCIA比千里眼一個信封 入面有卡寫住<br />\n火星，感興趣時間大約公元前1百萬<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/044947_d04ff1d7b829502c4f46a24a8e8a5486.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F044947_d04ff1d7b829502c4f46a24a8e8a5486.png&h=596fcb33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n信封從來冇打開過 CIA從來冇講入面有咩<br />\nCIA第一個指示係要千里眼根據信封入而既要求（潛意識上）<br />\n去呢個座標<br />\n40.89north<br />\n9.55west<br />\n（座標係CIA即場口講）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/050005_337160f26f8ff884e1d4158d13b3cba4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F050005_337160f26f8ff884e1d4158d13b3cba4.png&h=02a692c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個千里話見倒金字塔 黃咁咁 好多雲<br />\n。。。<br />\n就係咁9頁內容都係個CIA講下D座標<br />\n叫千里眼講見倒座標果度有咩。<br />\n<br />\n以下係其餘內容既部份翻譯：<br />\nCIA叫千里眼'望'最後一set座標<br />\n（文件紀錄上係最後，但唔知呢個文件係咪紀錄完整全個interview）<br />\n千里眼：有幾個（重疊？）金字塔。。。 好大風 入去見倒一D就死既'人'<br />\n。。。<br />\n千里眼：D'人'好似等緊一D野。。。好似係等另一堆人 有另一堆人 去左好遠搵新既地方生存<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/050554_cabdddc9ce318afc626c7426ed58c2dc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F050554_cabdddc9ce318afc626c7426ed58c2dc.png&h=078e2463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住個CIA叫千里眼 問等緊果D人 知唔知千里眼係邊個<br />\n同埋問有冇野可以幫倒佢地<br />\n。。。<br />\n千里眼：果D人以為我係一個幻覺。。<br />\n千里眼：D金字塔好似幫佢地擋風<br />\n。。。<br />\nCIA：走左果D人去左邊？<br />\n千里眼：佢地好似響架船入面 D牆好滑 D金屬好伶<br />\n。。。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/050717_e99e3bee860d6d1e3a01b7bc47de5ebc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F050717_e99e3bee860d6d1e3a01b7bc47de5ebc.png&h=f020cfef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n___________________________<br />\n部份三<br />\n<strong>可以上Google Mars Check番文件提到既座標</strong><br />\n要下載最新Google Earth <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uCpD65wmh90&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=4m29s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuCpD65wmh90%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26t%3D4m29s&d=KVXReHL18IQ%2FliS%2BhPGK%2Fp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=05330b99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uCpD65wmh90&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=4m29s</a><br />\n呢條片可以show倒<br />\n座標上真係有千里眼講既金字塔！<br />\n___________________________<br />\n究竟<br />\nQ1。千里眼呢種能力係堅定流？<br />\n英文：Remote Viewing<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harold_E._Puthoff\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FHarold_E._Puthoff&d=KVXReHL18IQ%2FliS%2BhPGK%2Fp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=3c3a09dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harold_E._Puthoff</a><br />\n呢個Harold博士（電子工程）都係當年有參與果個研究<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EsRreqmQWN8?t=2m40s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEsRreqmQWN8%3Ft%3D2m40s&d=KVXReHL18IQ%2FliS%2BhPGK%2Fp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=fcd47d6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EsRreqmQWN8?t=2m40s</a><br />\n片6：12佢提問 量子力學同人類意識有咩關係<br />\n（因為量子可以時空跳來跳去 咁意識可唔可以？）<br />\nQ2。火星公元前一百萬年係咪曾經有'人'？<br />\nQ3。人類祖先係咪來自火星。。。？"},{"pid":"74c4342a9ead9f119afbc16362699806fb11d07b","tid":751383,"uid":107156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T22:47:26.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"2e7e61385da888f476b40d7ff0e86654ebed4978","tid":751383,"uid":62443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T00:36:40.000Z","msg":"星門計畫<br />\n有冇中文片睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82be4ae2ccbc28d7c9e20937c36877abda78421d","tid":751383,"uid":78384,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T00:50:59.000Z","msg":"留名等睇"},{"pid":"19fa41d0317e79606515c9588220c2db6c7fe1f3","tid":751383,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T01:07:42.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"b9cc40ce18d8a7b5a7f5aa93900383aec2e548c6","tid":751383,"uid":85307,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T01:18:06.000Z","msg":"remote viewing感覺上叫做最易<br />\n訓練下內在感官only<br />\nESP人地鬼佬已經玩咗好多年"},{"pid":"4159dfbbe3f07775a2f5ce15820fbe9b5bf09b2c","tid":751383,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T01:25:48.000Z","msg":"密探睥死羊"},{"pid":"f678c0ef01f59592e8a8d0c1174fe652dde47bea","tid":751383,"uid":181809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T01:28:07.000Z","msg":"powpow有講過 但好似唔同人"},{"pid":"83c1dc9d764eb46a2c32dc8749922c708a5a4201","tid":751383,"uid":86684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T01:28:39.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"43d0704d61a6dbc7243259c009fd795cb96c9798","tid":751383,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:24:39.000Z","msg":"CIA remote viewing guide<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cia.gov/library/readingroom/docs/CIA-RDP96-00787R000300110001-8.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cia.gov%2Flibrary%2Freadingroom%2Fdocs%2FCIA-RDP96-00787R000300110001-8.pdf&d=KVXReHL18IQ%2FliS%2BhPGK%2Fp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=e4695f9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cia.gov/library/readingroom/docs/CIA-RDP96-00787R000300110001-8.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"56a70f383adcb0bf4d243b17f2771ab81cca23b7","tid":751383,"uid":94157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T08:47:54.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"806513aba710ebe812933240c440ab8525ea2b93","tid":751383,"uid":57410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T09:05:02.000Z","msg":"西藏高曾咪識千里眼 他心通呢d基本野啦<br />\n<br />\n紅色警戒都係抄佢"}]}